content: If you have copied all messages from IMAP folders to Local Folders, you have prevented loss of the messages. To put the folders on the desktop computer, just - exit thunderbird on laptop - copy the Mail\Local Folders folders of interest to a USB stick - on desktop, create the same dummy folders in thunderbird - exit TB and copy the folders from USB to overwrite the dummy folders.
creator: davidsk
